      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get around town? This car has plenty of character and offers a great opportunity for someone mechanically inclined to bring it back to its former glory! While it definitely needs some TLC and significant repairs to be at its best, it's a fantastic value for anyone looking for a low-cost entry into vehicle ownership.",
