    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are functioning properly. You can expect a solid, road-ready car that requires no immediate major repairs.",
