    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find for the discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior remains in pristine, original state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, having been meticulously stored and cared for. You will not find a more perfect example of this model on the market.",
